- `public static int add(int a, int b)` — Adds two numbers.
- `public static int multiply(int a, int b)` — Multiplies via repeated addition.
- `public static boolean isEven(int n)` — Mutual recursion: delegates to isOdd.
- `public static boolean isOdd(int n)` — Mutual recursion: delegates to isEven.

